:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_13d60d4ddd116661e52c043c991db18f.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110640933_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_f393a0cfd28cc5a425c2a1a85bb9c396.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Alexey Agarishev </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：与白宫进行美国债务上限谈判的共和党谈判代表帕特里克麦克亨利周六表示，提高政府借款限额的协议可能会在数小时或数天内达成。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “这是几个小时或几天，我不知道什么时候，”北卡罗来纳州的代表在华盛顿告诉记者。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">国会中的共和党人一直在推动削减开支，以换取提高 31.4 万亿美元<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230508/what-should-americans-brace-for-on-the-brink-of-default-1110191569.html" target="_blank">的债务上限</a>。 McHenry 说，仍有待处理的问题清单已经减少到只有几个。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他说：“很长一段时间以来，我们的名单很长。我没有预料到的是，很长一段时间以来，我们的名单都很短。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">财政部长珍妮特耶伦<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/yellen-us-has-until-at-least-june-5-to-hammer-debt-ceiling-deal-before-defaulting-1110618245.html" target="_blank">周五宣布</a>，国会领导人达成妥协的最后期限被推迟到 6 月 5 日。她警告说，如果不能达成协议，美国将面临资金枯竭的风险。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 27 May 2023 16:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/republican-debt-ceiling-negotiator-says-deal-expected-in-hours-or-days-1110641092.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/republican-debt-ceiling-negotiator-says-deal-expected-in-hours-or-days-1110641092.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>债务上限</category><category>帕特里克麦克亨利</category><category>珍妮特·耶伦</category><category>白色的房子</category><category>共和党（美国）</category><category>美国国会</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Russian Air Defenses Destroy Kiev's UK-Supplied Storm Shadow Cruise Missiles]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="media__video"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/css/videoplayer/videoplayer.min.css?9fe0c0742"><div class="video-player " style="padding-top: 56.25%;" data-nosnippet=""><video id="video_1110639936" data-import-id="26853620" data-media-id="1110639936" data-articleid="1110640471" data-title="Russian Air Defenses Destroy Kiev's UK-Supplied Storm Shadow Cruise Missiles" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/russian-air-defenses-destroy-kievs-uk-supplied-storm-shadow-cruise-missiles-1110640471.html" data-next-autoplay="false" data-length="26" playsinline="true" poster="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110639972_0:0:426:240_600x0_80_0_0_1579820f71ce7620b6750a954c899958.jpg" preload="none" class="video-js vjs-fluid" width="100%" height="100%"><p class="vjs-no-js">要观看此视频，请启用 JavaScript，并考虑升级到支持 HTML5 视频的网络浏览器</p></video><div class="video_info" data-customer-type="main" data-media-id="1110639936" data-import-id="26853620" data-article-id="1110640471" id="video_info__1110639936" data-video-length="26" data-video-type="" data-video-file-size="3273533" data-ads=""></div></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©人造卫星</div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">安德烈·德加林</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_dergalin_andrei/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:a.dergalin@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">尽管美国及其盟国继续向基辅政权提供武器，而基辅政权已经表现出使用这种硬件对付民用目标的意愿，但俄罗斯军方一直表明它可以对抗西方提供的任何东西。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">虽然乌克兰军队倾向于将西方为其武器库提供的​​每一个新武器都视为游戏规则的改变者，但随着俄罗斯军队迅速学会如何应对这些威胁，他们的喜悦往往是短暂的。最近从英国得到的一枚<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230515/details-of-uks-storm-shadow-cruise-missile-revealed--1110376749.html" target="_blank">风暴影子</a>巡航导弹基辅也不例外。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">昨天，在乌克兰冲突地区作战的俄罗斯防空部队击落了两枚<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230512/what-are-storm-shadow-missiles-and-how-can-russia-defeat-them-1110288372.html" target="_blank">风暴暗影</a>导弹，以及其他几个空中威胁。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">俄罗斯国防部在一份声明中说：“防空系统拦截了两枚风暴暗影远程巡航导弹、19 枚 HIMARS 多管火箭炮和两枚 HARM 反辐射导弹。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110640471" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/russian-air-defenses-destroy-kievs-uk-supplied-storm-shadow-cruise-missiles-1110640471.html?share-block=1110640791" data-title="&quot;Air defense systems have intercepted two Storm Shadow long-range cruise missiles, 19 HIMARS MLRS rockets and two HARM anti-radiation missiles,&quot; the Russian Ministry of Defense said in a statement."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，俄罗斯卢甘斯克人民共和国、顿涅茨克人民共和国和扎波罗热地区的俄罗斯防空部队击落了约 12 架由基辅部队操作的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/advanced-russian-ew-systems-reportedly-take-out-10000-ukrainian-drones-per-month--1110553449.html" target="_blank">无人机</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国及其盟国向乌克兰提供了价值数十亿美元的武器和军事装备——包括小型武器、大炮、多管火箭发射系统和<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/was-nasams-successful-in-ukraine-1110585927.html" target="_blank">防空系统</a>，煽动该国持续冲突的火势，并有效地帮助延长乌克兰平民的战斗和苦难。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 27 May 2023 16:16:57 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/russian-air-defenses-destroy-kievs-uk-supplied-storm-shadow-cruise-missiles-1110640471.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/russian-air-defenses-destroy-kievs-uk-supplied-storm-shadow-cruise-missiles-1110640471.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>巡航导弹</category><category>防空</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[IRS Whistleblower Closing in on DoJ's 'Cover-Up' of Hunter Biden Case]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110640188" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0a/1110232556_0:0:3071:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_6011c262e7f3c5e5b535e0c87c3f8610.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110232538" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/irs-whistleblower-closing-in-on-dojs-cover-up-of-hunter-biden-case-1110640188.html?share-img=1110232538"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Patrick Semansky</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Hunter Biden，乔·拜登总统的儿子，2023 年 2 月 4 日星期六，在纽约州锡拉丘兹的汉考克空军国民警卫队基地，与拜登总统一起走下空军一号后走向一辆车队车辆</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Hunter Biden, son of President Joe Biden, walks to a motorcade vehicle after stepping off Air Force One with President Biden, Saturday, Feb. 4, 2023, at Hancock Field Air National Guard Base in Syracuse, N.Y. - Sputnik International, 1920, 27.05.2023" title="2023 年 2 月 4 日，星期六，在纽约州锡拉丘兹的汉考克空军国民警卫队基地，乔·拜登总统的儿子亨特·拜登在与拜登​​总统一起走下空军一号后走向一辆车队车辆。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0a/1110232556_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_0b7cd968f3a4d1adc765a2285a2a2e49.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0a/1110232556_0:161:3071:1888_640x0_80_0_0_7d8fa207773eadb1fb84bcff6c40854d.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0a/1110232556_0:161:3071:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_7519ef5441bce97ec9ce139e07481d1e.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0a/1110232556_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_0b7cd968f3a4d1adc765a2285a2a2e49.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Patrick Semansky </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶卡捷琳娜布林诺娃</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_ekaterina_blinova/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.blinova@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">美国国税局举报人周五就亨特·拜登刑事税务调查的起源以及司法部 (DoJ) 自 2020 年以来对调查的干预向美国国会作证。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 5 月 26 日，美国国税局监督刑事调查员转为举报人加里·沙普利 (Gary Shapley) 出现在美国众议院筹款委员会面前。他提供了 7 份重磅文件，共 23 页，以证实他关于第一个儿子税务犯罪调查明显“优待”的说法。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">总而言之，沙普利作证了大约六个小时，并回答了共和党和民主党立法者的提问。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">除了详述美国国税局调查亨特·拜登的证据和前提外，该代理人提交的文件还表明，至少从 2020 年开始，美国司法部官员多次试图阻挠和干扰他的调查。根据 Shapley 的说法，美国国税局和联邦调查局的特工都对司法部的干预感到担忧。美国国税局举报人自 2020 年 1 月起监督税务调查。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">沙普利告诉 CBS 新闻：“当我接管这项特殊调查时，我立即看到了与正常流程的偏差。这远远超出了我过去所经历的规范。” “在司法部的指导下，有多个步骤进展缓慢——完全没有完成。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110640188" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/irs-whistleblower-closing-in-on-dojs-cover-up-of-hunter-biden-case-1110640188.html?share-block=1110640191" data-title="&quot;When I took control of this particular investigation, I immediately saw deviations from the normal process. It was way outside the norm of what I've experienced in the past,&quot; Shapley told CBS News. &quot;There were multiple steps that were slow-walked – were just completely not done – at the direction of the Department of Justice.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在美国国税局工作了 14 年的沙普利本周早些时候揭露了真相。此前，他的身份被隐藏在举报人保护之下。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">事实上，他的“受保护披露”始于 2020 年夏天：当时他开始注意到美国司法部处理此案的方式存在违规行为，但随后没有任何反应。 2022 年 10 月，沙普利会见了负责亨特·拜登调查的特拉华州联邦检察官戴维·韦斯，并向他通报了他对该案处理的担忧。此后，Shapley 和他的 IRS 团队不再受邀参加有关调查的检察团队会议。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2023 年 4 月，美国国税局的举报人向美国立法者通报了亨特·拜登税务犯罪调查期间的明显违规行为，指责美国联邦检察官干预调查并据称试图包庇第一个儿子。作为回应，众议院筹款委员会“免除了”沙普利及其律师的6103税收隐私义务，以便他们可以向美国国会提供有关亨特·拜登的所有证据，以供进一步审查。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，在这些事态发展之后，国税局资深人士和他的 12 名下属突然被驱逐出调查。沙普利的下属试图查明这一决定背后的原因——却被美国国税局官员吓倒了。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国立法者致信美国国税局局长丹尼尔韦费尔，要求澄清这似乎是对美国国税局举报人的报复行为。 5 月 17 日，维尔菲尔回应称，他与将沙普利的团队从亨特·拜登调查中除名无关，并证实<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/commissioner-points-finger-at-doj-for-purging-hunter-biden-irs-whistleblowers-1110564590.html" target="_blank">是司法部</a>下达了此类命令。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 5 月 25 日，司法机构主席吉姆乔丹写信给司法部长梅里克加兰，敦促他解释为什么美国国税局举报人小组被暂停调查，并警告说委员会不会容忍司法部“对这个或任何其他举报人的报复行为”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>乔丹强调说：“该部门据称将国税局举报人从正在进行的调查中除名的努力可能是美国法律禁止的报复行动。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110640188" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/irs-whistleblower-closing-in-on-dojs-cover-up-of-hunter-biden-case-1110640188.html?share-block=1110640200" data-title="&amp;quot;The department’s alleged efforts to remove an IRS whistleblower from an ongoing investigation could be a retaliatory action prohibited under United States law,&amp;quot; Jordan stressed."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">围绕 2018 年发起的亨特·拜登税务调查的争议并不是<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/whats-behind-irs-turning-blind-eye-to-hunter-biden-and-hillary-clinton-cases-1110541656.html" target="_blank">第一个儿子明显在政治上掩盖事实</a>的唯一例子。此前，根据埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的重磅炸弹 Twitter 文件，FBI 特工在 2020 年 10 月协助压制了《纽约邮报》 <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html" target="_blank">关于亨特“来自地狱的笔记本电脑”的报道</a>，当时他的父亲乔·拜登 (Joe Biden) 正在竞选总统。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，应当时的拜登竞选活动高级特工安东尼·布林肯的要求，多达<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230516/durhams-report-will-make-it-difficult-for-us-intel-community-to-meddle-in-2024-race-1110404217.html" target="_blank">51 名前高级情报官员</a>将来自亨特笔记本电脑的诅咒材料标记为“俄罗斯虚假信息”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在控制了众议院之后，共和党立法者承诺查明亨特·拜登的税务犯罪，怀疑他与外国势力进行影响力兜售计划，并且乔·拜登明显参与了他儿子的“生意”。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 27 May 2023 15:36:39 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/irs-whistleblower-closing-in-on-dojs-cover-up-of-hunter-biden-case-1110640188.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/irs-whistleblower-closing-in-on-dojs-cover-up-of-hunter-biden-case-1110640188.html<category>美洲</category><category>亨特·拜登</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>特拉华州</category><category>众议院筹款委员会</category><category>共和党人</category><category>联邦调查局</category><category>国税局 (IRS)</category><category>我们</category></item></channel></rss>